
Overview of noun pedestal

The noun pedestal has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (1) base, pedestal, stand -- (a support or foundation; "the base of the lamp")
2. pedestal -- (a position of great esteem (and supposed superiority); "they put him on a pedestal")
3. pedestal, plinth, footstall -- (an architectural support or base (as for a column or statue))
